OL,3,CTeachers speak out on 'unsustainable'
OL,4,Cworkloads after unions vote for strike
OL,6,FTeachers in Northern Ireland have told
OL,7,FUTV they are exhausted having to face
OL,8,F"unsustainable" workloads with many
OL,9,Fworking in in"crumbling" buildings in
OL,10,Fneed of investment.
OL,12,FIn a majority vote all three teaching
OL,13,Funions voted for strike action and
OL,14,Faction short of strike.
OL,16,FTeachers in England received a 5.5%
OL,17,Fpay rise for 2024-25 from the
OL,18,Fgovernment in September.
