OL,6,FStudents in Northern Ireland have
OL,7,Fbecome increasingly anxious with more
OL,8,Freports of children suffering mental
OL,9,Fhealth issues.
OL,11,FUna Kelly who is a Head of Year in
OL,12,FCross and Passion College in
OL,13,FBallycastle added: "There are so many
OL,14,Fdemands on teachers, not only what we
OL,15,Fdo in the classroom but there are so
OL,16,Fmany factors that demand time."
OL,18,FUna highlighted how the coronavirus
OL,19,Fpandemic had a negative impact on
OL,20,Fyoung people.
